name: Cosy single-family home with garden
description:
Nestled in a peaceful suburban neighborhood on the outskirts of London, this delightful four-bedroom detached family home offers the perfect blend of comfort, space, and tranquility.
The property features a spacious open-plan living area with large windows that allow plenty of natural light to flood the space. A modern fully-equipped kitchen with high-end appliances opens onto a cozy dining area, making it ideal for family gatherings. The house also boasts a separate lounge with a fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.
Upstairs, the home comprises four generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms share a stylish family bathroom with contemporary fittings.
One of the standout features of this home is the beautifully landscaped garden, offering a large lawn, a patio area for outdoor dining, and a variety of mature trees and flowerbeds. The garden provides an idyllic setting for relaxation and entertainment, perfect for families or those who enjoy spending time outdoors.
Additional benefits include a private driveway with ample parking space, a garage, and easy access to local schools, parks, and transport links to central London.
This charming home is ideal for families looking for a peaceful retreat while remaining well-connected to the city
